{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":":right","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:right","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>:right</code></strong> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\">伪类</a>必须与<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/At-rule\">@规则</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@page\"><code>@page</code></a> 一起配套使用，表示打印文档的所有右页。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* 当打印时会选择所有文档右页 */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@page</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>right</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2in 3in<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>这里的“左”或“右”不是固定的，取决与文档的写作方向。如果第一页主要文字方向是从左到右的，那么它就是<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:right\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>:right</code></a>右页，反之它就是<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:left\"><code>:left</code></a>左页。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> Note: 可通过 <code>bdo</code> 标签 的 <code>dir</code> 属性改变文字方向。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 此伪类只能用于更改页面的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/padding\"><code>padding</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border\"><code>border</code></a>, and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/background\"><code>background</code></a> 属性。其它属性都将被忽略，只会影响页框，不会影响文档内容。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">@page:right{\n    margin: * *;\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@page</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>right</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2in 3in<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-page/#left-right-first","title":"Proposals for the future of CSS Paged Media"}],"query":"css.selectors.right"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"css.selectors.right","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:right/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@page\"><code>@page</code></a></li>\n  <li>Other page-related pseudo-classes: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:first\"><code>:first</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:left\"><code>:left</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":":right CSS 伪类必须与@规则 @page 一起配套使用，表示打印文档的所有右页。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":":right","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":":right","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":":right","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":":right","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":":right","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/_colon_right","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/_colon_right/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e5